			dependencies: ["41BA52E902F54F5F"]
			description: ["Superconductors negate any EU loss over distance. This means you can run a superconductor cable as far as you want and you won't lose any EU. They also allow better amperages compared to normal cables. (PS: There are only superconductor wires and not cables. You will not take any damage touching the wire since there is no EU loss.)"]
			id: "2362662AB695FE15"
